column5: Odd because his name is Ian haha

Reading the title of this made me happy and sad. Happy because I’ve never related to anything more and I’m glad I’m not the only one. Sad because other people feel the way I do. I hope things get well for you OP
Why do I think this is so fucking cool

I have a job offering as a horse wrangler in Montana. That would start in May, which I’m excited for. But in the mean time I have no choice but to stay with my Scumbag roommate. I just hope I make it till May.
The cameras on a dresser behind the closet, not in the closet. I’m positive it’s on. It’s a motion sensor and he can control where it looks from his phone and gets alerted when it senses something
Exactly. And I don’t have any other place to go. I’m currently out of state and I will be confronting him when I come back home.
I obviously will... but he has screenshots of me and stuff..
